name: Regina Baidoo
description: i’m Regina Baidoo by name…am a very easy going lady without know gamesam 5’8 tall..I am a fun loving girl. I love the outdoors, board games, music and movies. I am serious, honest and open minded. I am here seeking friendship which can turn into something serious, , I am a confident woman, honest, reliable, kindness, interesting, generous, outgoing, have a sense of humor, good listener, have a strong values, honest, dependable and passionate about life and fun woman with passion for life. I do feel happy in my own skin.I am a broad and open minded, exciting, humorous woman, I enjoy happiness and I love making people happy as well.I value life and I love improving it, cos life is a gift and should be treasured..family is very important to me.I would like to find a man whom I would see ‘through rose coloured glasses’, who was intelligent and could be admired for his thinking, and he own unique abilities. One whom I could offer encouragement, support and unconditional respect and love. I seek a life with a special partner that exists in a place of peace and harmony, where I would consider there existed a ‘calm pond’ where both of us would be relaxed and develop an instinctive understanding of each other. A life where the work was shared so that time to ‘have fun’ together was not lost. Above all to pursue a dream for true love that is a fulfillment of mutual desires which inspires commitment and devotion..I want to meet someone who will be there for me and care of my daughter and trust me and support me in everything
